{"tid":1619407,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"David Webb：緊急法可能違憲　籲大律師公會提司法覆核","createTime":"2019-10-04T07:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T10:26:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"913787c34176c45edc217d6c273b32b2b29b5d8d","tid":1619407,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:53:18.000Z","msg":"多家媒體引述消息指，政府決定引用《緊急法》訂立《禁蒙面法》，預料稍後三時記者會上將會公佈詳情。香港股壇長毛 David Webb 表示，引用《緊急法》立法違反《基本法》規定的立法行政分權原則，《緊急法》本身可能違憲。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb 指，《緊急法》條文賦權特首通過任何其認為對公眾利益有利的法例，他質疑條文涵蓋範圍過廣，有可能違反《基本法》。他認為大律師公會或其他人士應立即入禀申請司法覆核，並要求法院頒布禁制令，暫緩引用《緊急法》。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb 又指，就算特首林鄭月娥成功引用《緊急法》訂立《反蒙面法》，嚴刑峻法亦無法解決問題根源，即香港特首及立法會的民主問責性已存在「赤字」。David Webb 表示，相信有人將針對政府引用《緊急法》提出司法覆核，他又呼籲政府立即啟動民主化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/r-david-webb-%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E9%81%95%E6%86%B2-%E7%B1%B2%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fr-david-webb-%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%2586%25B2-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8%2F&d=pX%2F9NM0RDLHEoMpKo%2B7ToQEiaVT8aWta%2BTWQuzHxyy8%3D&h=87e22cbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fr-david-webb-%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%2586%25B2-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8%2F&h=c560ba28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/r-david-webb-%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E9%81%95%E6%86%B2-%E7%B1%